---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Top Narvar Alternatives: 4 Post-Purchase Software Providers to Consider - parcelLab"
  description="Explore top Narvar alternatives that ecommerce brands should consider when evaluating post-purchase software platforms."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Post-Purchase</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Top Narvar Alternatives: 4 Post-Purchase Software Providers to Consider</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2023-03-20">March 20, 2023</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>10 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          This article explores top Narvar alternatives that ecommerce brands should consider when evaluating post-purchase software platforms, examining their features, pros, cons, and competitive offerings.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">1. parcelLab (Top Choice)</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The only truly global enterprise post-purchase software provider. Trusted by over 700 brands including IKEA, Chico's, H&M, and Yeti, managing post-purchase experience across 175 countries with 350+ carriers. Implementation completed in 30 days or less with fully white-labeled communications.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">2. AfterShip</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Comprehensive post-purchase platform headquartered in Singapore providing shipment tracking, delivery prediction, shipping protection, and returns management. Plans start at $11/month for 100 shipments.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">3. Malomo</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          A newer post-purchase platform primarily serving Shopify merchants. Offers white-labeled emails and tracking pages, but limited to Shopify with no native returns capabilities.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">4. WISMOlabs</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Established in 2019 offering customizable tracking pages, shipment notifications, reporting, and delivery date predictions. Primarily targets small businesses in the United States.
        </p>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          While Narvar provides comprehensive post-purchase capabilities, alternatives exist to address common concerns. The choice depends on specific business requirements including budget, integration needs, and desired level of customization.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
